{"tid":393330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"補習中介你幾撚時俾車撞？","createTime":"2017-09-09T07:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T13:16:38.000Z","uid":132401,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52c8771aaeddc36e538f2f96ffac558e87664d06","tid":393330,"uid":132401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T07:27:26.000Z","msg":"依家啲補習中介好撚奸架 <br />\n乜撚野口頭承諾啊, 取消費啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係識兇鳩啲大學生同啱啱岀社會嘅後生<br />\n乜柒<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">小額錢債審裁處</span></span>  識野嘅就知唔洗驚<br />\n因為佢同你都冇得請律師 兼且唔係僱傭關政府兩邊都理唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n學生:我打上嚟係想提下唔好俾人大到/俾人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家長: 盡量補曬先俾中介費啦 同埋最好一開始放一星期一堂先 導師俾人食少啲又補得開心啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再者廢事導師走佬 你唔好諗撚住中介退翻俾你啊 驚你追到噴血冇人照顧你寶貝仔啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:經過唔少中介接補習 最仆街係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">uni-tutor </span></span>你要話cut堂所以少咗中介錢？佢地cut9你線添啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  朋友發夢聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班中介呃呃埋埋咁多錢俾你地買藥食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c6e35456e287af5e70b4890abc4f8f7b5960cb","tid":393330,"uid":132401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"啱啱開學 希望翗啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ff1c8eff5d6e666b8fab40febf6cb26dcb1d36","tid":393330,"uid":132401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,